name: TC_03_02_02 | Verify navigation to Home page from fromFooterDomainSearch
description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterDomainSearch.
descriptionHtml: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterDomainSearch.

testStage.description: To verify that user can navigate to Home page from fromFooterDomainSearch.

steps.name: Preconditions: Login as a registered user
Click on "Domain Name Search" link in Footer.
Verify user is redirected to Home page
Verify that Home page has "Millions of domains with the ultimate privacy protection" heading.
